{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UjxsPt4HCEneEHtNWfPi8W","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I've successfully read all five files. Here's the complete structure with full content and line numbers:\n\n---\n\n## File 1: ActiveMatchView.tsx\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/ActiveMatchView.tsx`\n\nThis component displays the active match through phases (created, ready, countdown, flipping, complete). It manages:\n- Lock timeout tracking (2-minute timeout for VRF resolution)\n- Countdown timer state for flip animation\n- Win/lose animations with particles\n- Timeout cancel button for stalled matches\n- Phase-specific UX for each game state\n\n**Key exports**: `ActiveMatchView` (functional component)\n\n---\n\n## File 2: CoinflipPage.tsx\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CoinflipPage.tsx`\n\nThis is the main page component that orchestrates the entire coinflip UI. It:\n- Integrates `CoinflipProvider` context\n- Manages sidebar with tier/side selection\n- Shows **fairness info sidebar** (lines 223-256) with Match ID, Seed Hash, Server Seed, and Block Hash\n- Displays history modal with full fairness section (lines 470-515) including VRF Proof\n- Links to `/fairness` page for verification (line 518)\n- Handles hero/loser states and sidebar game info\n\n**Key fairness elements**:\n- Lines 223-256: `coinflip-sidebar__fairness` section in active game sidebar\n- Lines 470-515: `coinflip-history-modal__section` fairness section in history modal\n\n---\n\n## File 3: verification.ts\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts`\n\nThis is the fairness verification utility. It:\n- Exports `verifyMatch()` function that takes a `claimTxSignature` and `connection`\n- Parses the MatchSettled event from transaction logs\n- Extracts randomness bytes and re-derives coin flip result\n- Validates winner is one of the two players\n- Confirms VRF fulfillment by checking the Orao randomness account\n- Returns `VerificationResult` with all proof data\n\n**Key interface**:\n```typescript\nexport interface VerificationResult {\n  verified: boolean;\n  creator: string;\n  opponent: string;\n  winner: string;\n  randomnessHex: string;\n  derivedResult: \"heads\" | \"tails\";\n  vrfFulfilled: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## File 4: CoinflipContext.tsx\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx`\n\nThis is the state management layer. It:\n- Manages active match, open matches, claimable matches, and user history\n- Handles tier/side selection\n- Provides actions: createMatch, joinMatch, cancelMatch, timeoutCancel, claimPayout\n- Implements polling (2s when waiting for VRF, 5s otherwise)\n- Uses `sendAndConfirm()` helper for transaction confirmation\n- Manages loading states and error messages\n- Exports `CoinflipContextValue` interface and `useCoinflip()` hook\n\n**Key state**:\n- `activeMatch: UIMatch | null`\n- `openMatches: UIMatch[]`\n- `claimableMatches: UIMatch[]`\n- `error: string | null`\n\n---\n\n## File 5: types.ts\n**Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/types.ts`\n\nThis defines the core types. Key interfaces:\n\n```typescript\nexport type CoinSide = \"heads\" | \"tails\";\nexport type CoinflipPhase = \"created\" | \"ready\" | \"countdown\" | \"flipping\" | \"complete\";\n\nexport interface UIMatch {\n  id: string;\n  tier: Tier;\n  entryAmount: number;\n  player1: string;\n  player1Side: CoinSide;\n  player2: string | null;\n  player2Side: CoinSide | null;\n  phase: CoinflipPhase;\n  createdAt: number;\n  lockedAt?: number;\n  countdownStartedAt?: number;\n  completedAt?: number;\n  result: CoinSide | null;\n  winner: string | null;\n  claimed: boolean;\n  payoutAmount: number;\n  \n  // Provably Fair fields\n  seedHash: string;\n  serverSeed?: string;\n  vrfProof?: string;\n  blockHash?: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary for Fairness Verification UI Implementation\n\nThe structure shows:\n\n1. **Fairness data is already in `UIMatch`** (lines 37-42 in types.ts): seedHash, serverSeed, vrfProof, blockHash\n2. **Sidebar shows fairness info** when activeMatch exists (CoinflipPage lines 223-256)\n3. **History modal shows detailed fairness** (CoinflipPage lines 470-515)\n4. **Verification utility is ready** (verification.ts) to be called with claimTxSignature\n5. **Missing**: A dedicated `/fairness` page that uses `verification.ts` to verify past matches\n\nThe fairness verification UI should:\n- Accept a match ID or transaction signature from the user\n- Call `verifyMatch()` from the context\n- Display the verification result (randomness, derived result, VRF fulfillment status)\n- Show pass/fail status prominently"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aee821f622326b1f6 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 48288\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 15852</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"59ba0125-0f76-4103-95f0-9eaafc029fda","uuid":"59d021c7-344a-4f4f-888a-3fcc3a84b359","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the following files in full and report their contents:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/components/ActiveMatchView.tsx`\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CoinflipPage.tsx`\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts`\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx`\n5. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/types.ts`\n\nFor each file, provide the full content with line numbers. I need to understand the exact structure to add a fairness verification UI.","agentId":"aee821f622326b1f6","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I've successfully read all five files. Her